g.text: Social Media Sharing & Viral Content Distribution
Instantly share BigScreen content across major social platforms to boost engagement and bring in new users.
Increases user acquisition through organic social sharing.
Enables AI-powered auto-clipping for viral moments.
Lets creators promote their live streams, NFTs, and content seamlessly.
Rewards users for driving traffic through referral and engagement programs.
Users can share clips, watchlists, and NFTs to Twitter, Instagram, TikTok, and Facebook.
Automatically detects key moments (exciting scenes, big reactions) and suggests shareable clips.
Users can add custom messages when sharing.
Users can tokenize and sell iconic moments from live events.
Track the number of clicks, shares, and conversions per user.
